  "title": "1 Year UAT - Group Payment Operations (Up to $5,500)  #NJN",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Tampines</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>9am to 6pm (Mondays to Fridays)</strong></em></p><ul><li>Collaborate with business analysts, project managers, and end-users to understand business requirements and acceptance criteria.</li><li>Develop and execute UAT test plans, test cases, and test scripts based on business requirements.</li><li>Coordinate and facilitate UAT testing sessions with end-users and stakeholders.</li><li>Identify, document, and track defects and issues found during UAT.</li><li>Communicate test results and provide feedback to development and SD teams.</li><li>Ensure that all business requirements are met before product release.</li><li>Assist in the preparation of UAT test environments and data.</li><li>Support the resolution of issues and re-test fixes as needed.</li><li>Maintain detailed documentation of test cases, results, and defect logs.</li><li>Participate in continuous improvement of UAT processes and methodologies.</li></ul><p></p><p>Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc</p><p>CEI Reg. No. R23113787</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p>",
